47
00:04:32,040 --> 00:04:32,800
(I'm leaving.)

48
00:04:33,399 --> 00:04:34,120
(Rest assured.)

49
00:04:34,720 --> 00:04:36,120
(I will find the real killer)

50
00:04:36,720 --> 00:04:37,680
(and avenge you.)

51
00:04:43,839 --> 00:04:44,360
Hyah!

52
00:04:54,639 --> 00:04:55,439
Xuanzhi.

53
00:04:56,439 --> 00:04:57,360
