Wu Lingling.

61
00:07:56,639 --> 00:07:57,600
You dare come back?

62
00:07:57,800 --> 00:07:58,519
Why wouldn't I?

63
00:07:59,079 --> 00:08:00,240
I've done nothing wrong.

64
00:08:00,240 --> 00:08:01,879
You and Li Ya'er murdered Father.

65
00:08:02,240 --> 00:08:03,839
Today, you shall be executed.

66
00:08:05,879 --> 00:08:07,160
(Token)
Here is the imperial token.

67
00:08:07,319 --> 00:08:08,839
