74
00:08:19,800 --> 00:08:20,639
Shadow Guards.

75
00:08:20,879 --> 00:08:21,439
- Here.
- Here.

76
00:08:21,720 --> 00:08:22,560
Those who obstruct

77
00:08:22,560 --> 00:08:24,199
the investigation of Lord Wuwei's death

78
00:08:24,800 --> 00:08:25,800
shall be executed.

79
00:08:35,600 --> 00:08:36,360
Ya'er.

80
00:08:36,519 --> 00:08:37,240
Ya'er.

81
