94
00:10:32,799 --> 00:10:33,759
My father died from

95
00:10:33,759 --> 00:10:34,799
fighting Li Ya'er.

96
00:10:34,799 --> 00:10:35,759
That's the truth.

97
00:10:35,960 --> 00:10:37,039
You know your father's

98
00:10:37,039 --> 00:10:38,080
